Key features:

- trading view connectivity

## Install

`pip install talkytrend`

## How to use it

```
    trend = TalkyTrend()
    result = await trend.fetch_analysis()
    print(result) #BUY
    monitor = await trend.monitor_assets() #monitor change of trend

```

